    "On all datasets, the model is updated for around 300 steps-roughly 6 epochs for CoNLL 2003, 10 epochs for NCBI Disease and BC5CDR, and 15 epochs for PolyIE, with batch sizes adjusted from 16 to 64 accordingly."
